Class HiveSessionImplwithUGI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hive.service.cli.session.HiveSessionImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HiveSession, HiveSessionBase

    public class HiveSessionImplwithUGI
extends HiveSessionImpl
    HiveSessionImplwithUGI. HiveSession with connecting user's UGI and delegation token if required. Note: this object may be shared between threads in HS2.
